allowed-tools: SlashCommand(*), TodoWrite(*), Bash(*), Read(*), Write(*)
---

# Template Command - Generate Proposal Templates

## Overview

Simple command to convert Deal Transfer Excel files into technical proposal templates with reasoning and checklist files.

## Usage

```bash
/template generate deal <excel.xlsx>  # Main command
/template status                        # Check status
/template list                          # List recent
```

## Commands

### Generate Template

**Command**: `/template generate deal <excel.xlsx>`

**Description**: Generate proposal template, reasoning, and checklist from Deal Transfer Excel

**Example**:
```bash
/template generate deal DT_0109.xlsx
```

**Output**:
