❌ Error: S2 sheet not found
   Sheet: Technical
   Solution: Ensure Excel has S2 (Technical) sheet

❌ Error: Required Python libraries not found
   Libraries: pandas, openpyxl
   Solution: pip install pandas openpyxl

❌ Error: Extraction failed
   Reason: Unable to parse field "Customer Name"
   Solution: Check Excel field names match reference
```

